description: This is some bonus video we shot during Liam’s first photo shoot, so it is pretty much Liam at his horny best, in front of the camera for the first time and that mix of nerves and enthusiasm for showing off all rolled into one horny lad who is just so very casual on camera. Check out the bit where he has a semi on and flops it around in his boxers! Classic teasing from this naughty chav boy. We didn’t add photographs into this video and maybe we will mix up some of the future photo shoot videos, some with photos some without.
title: Bonus Video of Liam's Photo Shoot - One of our Most Popular Str8 Hunks Playing in the Sunshine
